    "description": "Complete API collection for the authentication service of Tekina Food Delivery app.\n\n**Base URL:** http://localhost:5000\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Register → auto-sets cookies\n2. Login → auto-sets cookies\n3. Use authenticated endpoints (me, logout)\n4. Refresh token when access token expires\n5. Forgot password → Reset password",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
