                "v1",
                "auth",
                "logout"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Logout the current user. Deletes the session from the database and clears auth cookies.\n\n**Method:** POST (not GET — to prevent CSRF via prefetch/crawlers).\n\nTries access token first; falls back to refresh token if access token is expired."
          },
          "response": []
